Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.07,0:24:33.33,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Mako, we can't lose on our home course.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.33,0:24:36.29,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,We're Road Racers.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.29,0:24:40.20,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}Ummm, Sayuki.  What will you do\Nafter Mako quits road racing?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.20,0:24:41.58,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep on racing!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.58,0:24:42.54,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.54,0:24:44.74,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}So you won't retire, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.74,0:24:46.88,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll race for a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.27,0:24:52.49,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Any cute guy...?\NAny cute guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.49,0:24:53.82,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Good-bye, Sayuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.82,0:24:57.61,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}Next time on Initial D: "A Hot Wind and Violent\NDrive on Usui's Mountain Pass."
