Dialogue: 1,0:24:55.04,0:24:59.98,MainStyle,,0000,0430,0260,,Next Time:
Dialogue: 1,0:24:55.04,0:24:59.98,MainStyle,,0175,0000,0190,,{\a1}A Hot Wind and Violent Drive\Non Usui's Mountain Pass
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.61,0:24:59.08,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't miss it!
